      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Estrazione della variabile globale 'tip-int'    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "CV"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      "tip-int"            to   s-var                  .
           move      "G"                  to   s-dop                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
