       fas-orc-500-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Return o Do                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       fas-orc-500-310.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      v-num                to   w-key-num-int          .
